{"tid":59900,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"揸睪龍爪手！支那男睪丸被緊捏數分鐘因此痛死","createTime":"2016-12-30T04:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-01T03:51:02.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"660bee62da052a335b3de2ad0699b739491f6330","tid":59900,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T04:54:13.000Z","msg":"大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n海南省海口一名40多歲的鄧姓女子，日前停電動車時和30多歲的李姓男子發生爭執，憤而以手緊抓他的睪丸數分鐘，還大喊，「捏死你，讓你以後不能生小孩。」導致李男因疼痛而休克，雖然經過搶救，仍不治死亡。<br />\n<br />\n▼演員雷洪在《夜市人生》的「北斗爆橘拳」；此圖與本案無關。（圖／翻攝自民視）<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/282/d282593.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F282%2Fd282593.jpg&h=d0fae229&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄧女2012年4月19日和丈夫前往國小接孩子放學時，把電動車停在李男的店門口，人民網指出，當時李的姐姐認為這樣會影響生意，雙方因此發生口角，李男看到此情形也從店內走出，兩方人馬扭打在一起。<br />\n<br />\n扭打時，鄧女先用木凳打李男的額頭，之後她的弟弟剛好路過，也拿了張木凳並加上拳頭攻擊李；雙方爭執過程中，鄧女一度倒在地上，她趁此時機狠狠抓住李的睪丸，致其死亡。經過鑑定，李男的死因是因為外力使陰囊劇烈疼痛，引起神經性休克死亡。<br />\n<br />\n海口市中級人民法院8日審理此案時，公訴單位認為鄧女與他弟弟的行為已經觸犯刑法，而且犯罪事實清楚，證據也充分，應該以故意傷害罪追究他們姐弟倆的刑事責任。"},{"pid":"8cc3af52b2b9ac74568cd1f0c9a3ceadc03c208b","tid":59900,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"爆丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0445f177b80fde742ad9f3105ee63d2bfe711c3","tid":59900,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T04:57:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爆丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40fa009351b25d5af0e2e895cf1499d0f70afd8d","tid":59900,"uid":20963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T04:59:45.000Z","msg":"扯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c091386e0e254a0c82d1e42258f9f92dbdce7a","tid":59900,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T01:08:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104281ffbb6dc6a6b6c35cd498b0f48d6444c414","tid":59900,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T02:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07272ddac0713d191c2c19fdb7e49a7be4b09d9a","tid":59900,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T02:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5e1b7284e314c1ac104a00f2d7c35b3633a224","tid":59900,"uid":29947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T03:31:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd0d72d9dbfefc2dd9fa499da2241c68598dab5","tid":59900,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T03:41:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>扯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我9縮左"},{"pid":"0f05369dab74d079ec9a8f4d1f19e3802c60a3c0","tid":59900,"uid":26047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T03:46:28.000Z","msg":"我諗無野痛苦得過爆丸死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8c1ed71561c39d7452eb9df463d4ee9102141a","tid":59900,"uid":9894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T03:51:02.000Z","msg":"▼演員雷洪在《夜市人生》的「北斗爆橘拳」；<span style=\"color: red;\">此圖與本案無關。</span>（圖／翻攝自民視）<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/282/d282593.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F282%2Fd282593.jpg&h=d0fae229&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解笑撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}